\c 8
\s Hwamanda ina dzokutanga dzinoridzwa
\p
\v 1 Wakati azarura chisimbiso chichinomwe, kunyarara kukavapo kudenga kunenge sehafu yeora.
\v 2 Ipapo ndakaona vatumwa vanomwe vamire pamberi paMwari; kukapiwa kwaari hwamanda nomwe.
\v 3 Zvino mumwe mutumwa wakauya, akamira paaritari, ane mudziyo wezvinonhuhwira wendarama; kukapiwa kwaari zvinonhuhwira zvizhinji kuti azvipe pamwechete neminyengetero yavatsvene vose pamusoro pearitari yendarama, yakanga iri pamberi pechigaro choushe.
\v 4 Uye utsi hwezvinonhuhwira hwakakwira pamberi paMwari hwuchibva muruoko rwomutumwa pamwe neminyengetero yavatsvene.
\v 5 Mutumwa akatora mudziyo wezvinonhuhwira, akauzadza nomoto wearitari, aka\add u\add*kandira panyika; ipapo kukavapo namanzwi nekutinhira nemheni nokudengenyeka kwenyika.
\v 6 Ipapo vatumwa vanomwe vakanga vane hwamanda nomwe vakazvigadzirira kuridza.
\v 7 Mutumwa wokutanga wakaridza, kukauya chimvuramabwe nomoto zvakavhenganiswa neropa, zvikakandirwa panyika; nechetatu chemiti chikatsva, nouswa unyoro hwose hwakapiswa.
\v 8 Zvino mutumwa wechipiri wakaridza, chimwe segomo guru rinopfuta nomoto chikakandwa mugungwa. Ipapo chetatu chegungwa chikava ropa;
\v 9 uye chetatu chezvisikwa zvakanga zviri zvipenyu mugungwa chikafa, nechetatu chezvikepe chikaparadzwa.
\v 10 Zvino mutumwa wechitatu wakaridza, kukawa nyeredzi huru kubva kudenga, ichipfuta semwenje, ikawira pamusoro pechetatu chenzizi napazvitubu zvemvura.
\v 11 Zita renyeredzi rakanga richinzi, Gavakava; ipapo chetatu chemvura chikava gavakava, vanhu vazhinji vakafa nemvura, nokuti yakanga yavaviswa.
\v 12 Zvino mutumwa wechina wakaridza, chetatu chezuva chikarohwa, nechetatu chomwedzi, nechetatu chenyeredzi, kuti chetatu chazvo chisvibiswe, uye kuti chetatu chamasikati chirege kuvhenekera, nousiku saizvozvo.
\v 13 Ipapo ndakatarira, ndikanzwa mutumwa achibhururuka napakati pedenga, achiti nenzwi guru: Muchaona nhamo, Muchaona nhamo, Muchaona nhamo, vagari vepanyika, nokuda kwamamwe manzwi ehwamanda avatumwa vatatu vachazoridza.
